<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Rejection Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Inline CSS */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
        }
        .reason {
            color: #ff0000;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your Student Account has been Rejected</h1>
        <p>Dear <%= user.name%>,</p>
        <p>We regret to inform you that your student account at  has been rejected by the administrator.</p>
        <p>Reason for rejection: <span class="reason"><%= reason %></span></p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further clarification, please feel free to contact our support team at .</p>
        <p>Thank you.</p>
        <p>Best regards Mr. Soumya Mukherjee,<br><br>H.O.D<br>Dept. Computer Science Engineering(Data Science)</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
